== Psychosis ==
Alabaster believes that he is doing divine work by sitting in a chat room 37 hours a day telling people that they are Satanists and deserve to die. He has no social life or friends. When proven wrong, he tends to show his deeply insane side, accompanied by [[emo]]-like pissing about everything.

He is also in favor of the use of [[Chinese]] [[Alternative Medicine|traditional medicine]] as opposed to things which actually work and have a grounding in reality. Jamming some sage stalks up his urethra may have helped his gonorrhea, but this does not prove the efficacy of Chinese medicine, which is grounded in [[bullshit]]. Experts agree that no amount of sage or incense will ever reduce Alabaster's anus to normal size.

